PrecisAuthority to (a) execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing Jean-Paul Hubert to sign the INTER-AMERICAN CONVENTION ON THE GRANTING OF CIVIL RIGHTS TO WOMEN and the INTER-AMERICAN CONVENTION ON THE GRANTING OF POLITICAL RIGHTS TO WOMEN, done at Bogata on May 2, 1948, and (b) to bring those conventions, as well as the CONVENTION ON THE NATIONALITY OF WOMEN, done at Montevideo on December 26, 1933, into force for Canada.
